Does anyone know how to adjust the style border radius of a `@HubSpot/linked_image` in a template? I’ve tried
```styles={
  border: {
    border_radius: 10
  }
},```
I’m pretty sure that format is right, I think the only thing wrong is the path to `border_radius`. I’ve tried `border_radius`, `radius`, `corner`, `corner_radius`, and `border_corner_radius` but no luck yet though. Maybe it’s not possible for the image module… `styles={}` with margin and padding works though.
